{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1781654395895,"sessionID":"ses_12d308fc1ffec7ld4UBuzRqOIR","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"call_8t9wevbp","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"README.md","content":"# Temperature Conversion CLI Tool\n\n## Installation\nInstall the package using pip:\n```bash\npip install temperature-converter\n```\n\n## Usage\nRun the CLI tool with the following syntax:\n```bash\ntemperature-converter [from_unit] [to_unit] [value]\n```\n\n## Available Units\n- `celsius` (°C)\n- `fahrenheit` (°F)\n- `kelvin` (K)\n\n## Examples\n```bash\ntemperature-converter celsius fahrenheit 25\ntemperature-converter fahrenheit celsius 98.6\ntemperature-converter celsius kelvin 0\n```"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/Users/nathangreen/Development/eddi-lab/llm-orc/scratch/spike-tau-long-horizon/A-f5/workspaces/A-f5-41c4633f/README.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"scratch/spike-tau-long-horizon/A-f5/workspaces/A-f5-41c4633f/README.md","time":{"start":1781654395883,"end":1781654395893}},"id":"prt_ed2e09bdc001fIhQS3vKTTrwqP","sessionID":"ses_12d308fc1ffec7ld4UBuzRqOIR","messageID":"msg_ed2dd98e5001iXKnOlV6dGzCN0"}}
